content:
Can private employers mandate vaccines?

Some private employers require vaccines, such as for influenza, for employees in health care settings. 

States may prohibit vaccine mandates as a condition of employment and require that employees can opt out. https://t.co/XePenGaqp6 https://t.co/QjgFb1qOaV
